<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="fasten-vt">fasten <strong><em>vt</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'fɑːsn/    美 /'fæsn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-vt-vi-do-up-vt">1.★ <strong>vt &amp; vi 系牢 (do up)；(门、窗等) 关住；vt 使固定：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was so fat that my pants wouldn't fasten.
我胖得连裤子都扣不上了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Ladies and gentlemen, please fasten your seat belts.
女士们，先生们，请系好安全带。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>With an oxygen tank fastened on his back, Larry dived from the boat into the middle of the ocean.
背上装好氧气罐，拉里从船上跳入了海中。</p><footer>2014 江西</footer></div></div>